data.description: This charming single-family home is 3 Beds, 2 Baths, 1976 square feet on one level with a private backyard and is one of the larger units in the subdivision. Enjoy the amenities which include a clubhouse and spacious pool area & spa. Located in the heart of St. George this home offers convenience with its close proximity to shopping centers, churches, hospitals, and a variety of restaurants.  Whether you're a first-time buyer, looking to retire, or considering a second home, this property could fit a diverse range of needs.
